# Formatted

```scss
@include nested-keyword-separator-line-comments(
	$arg: (
		a: 1px, // nested keyword map separator line
		b: 2px,
	)
);

@include closing-block-comments(
	$list: (
		1px,
		2px,
	)
	/* keyword list close */,
	$call: fn(1px, 2px) /* keyword call close */
);

```
